    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've got to check out this absolute beauty! I've taken such good care of this car, it honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It is in truly flawless condition\u2014spotless inside and out, garage-kept, and runs like an absolute dream. I'm so sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to be over the moon with how perfect it is. It\u2019s basically a brand-new car at a much better price. Come see it for yourself and fall in love!",
