    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in a climate-controlled garage and maintained with obsessive care. The exterior features a flawless factory finish, recently treated with a multi-stage ceramic coating that reflects like a mirror, without a single swirl mark or stone chip in sight. Inside, the cabin still carries that distinctive new-car scent; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and free of any creasing or wear. Every button, switch, and electronic feature operates with tactile precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history exclusively performed at the authorized dealership. Included are all original keys, manuals, and a pristine set of floor mats. This is a museum-quality example for the most discerning collector.",
      "price": 44500.0,
